# OmniEngine — Production-Grade Multi-Model Multi-Agent AI System

A Tier-1, production-ready conversational AI platform with dynamic model routing, agentic workflows, RAG memory, safety guardrails, and a streaming Next.js frontend.

## Proposed Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Frontend["Frontend (Next.js 14)"]
        UI[Chat UI] --> SSE[SSE Stream Handler]
        UI --> MD[Markdown Renderer]
        UI --> Charts[Chart Components]
    end

    subgraph API["API Layer (FastAPI)"]
        LB[Load Balancer] --> Auth[Auth Middleware]
        Auth --> Router[Model Router]
        Router --> Guard[Input Guardrails]
    end

    subgraph Agents["Agent Layer (LangGraph)"]
        Orch[Orchestrator / Supervisor] --> Plan[Planner Node]
        Plan --> Memory[Memory Agent]
        Plan --> Tools[Tool Calling Agent]
        Plan --> RAG[RAG Agent]
        Plan --> Eval[Evaluator Node]
    end

    subgraph Infra["Data & Infrastructure"]
        PG[(PostgreSQL)]
        RD[(Redis)]
        QD[(Qdrant)]
        MCP[MCP Tool Registry]
    end

    SSE <-->|WSS/SSE| LB
    Guard --> Orch
    Memory --> PG
    Memory --> RD
    RAG --> QD
    Tools --> MCP
    Eval --> Orch
```

